author: Andrew Backhouse
title: Chinese study finds coronavirus mutation has been vastly underestimated
description: Chinese study finds coronavirus mutation has been vastly underestimatednews.com.au
content:
The new coronavirus is able to quickly mutate and multiple strains could account for differing impacts around the world. Research by China’s top scientists found new strains of the virus not previously reported.
